description:
Josh Gates journeys across America uncovering the truth behind its greatest legends from outlaws and lost flights to missing heroes and hidden treasures. He dives deep into the past to reveal the mysteries of Jesse James, a vanished aircraft, WWII legends and more!

About Expedition Unknown: 
Josh Gates investigates the truth behind the world's most iconic and captivating legends. Leaving no stone unturned, his adventures take him around the globe as he immerses himself in the core locales linked to each tale.
